sentences: Calum Scott (born 12 October 1988) is a British singer and songwriter.
In April 2015, he became known worldwide after competing on the ITV talent contest Britain's Got Talent, where he performed his version of Robyn's hit "Dancing on My Own".
Scott later signed with Capitol and in 2017, released the single "You Are the Reason", which was included on his 2018 debut album Only Human, which reached number 4 on the UK Albums Chart.
